@103749 = ~Staff of Meldanen +4~/*Bâton de Meldanen*/
@103750 = ~Ce bâton était l'arme de Meldanen. Il est sans doute empreint de magie.~
@103751 = ~One of many staffs created by the mage Meldanen. Over his career he supplied gold to a small industry of adventurers that would bring him exotic materials for his workshop. In his later years he was not so charitable, and occasionally set two or more groups against each other to secure the most reasonable prices for himself. Recently he stopped the practice altogether, preferring that as few people knew of his experiments as possible.

