@104434 = ~Tomi "Grin" Undergallows is a halfling rogue and thief from Calimport. Tomi hails from Kalimshan and, like most locals, has followed the path of crime. Tomi is a master of lockpicking and detecting and disarming traps. He had an eventful youth, though all of his adventures involve stealing and girls. He spent the larger part of his years in Calimport in the employ of a powerful medusa, and one day she ordered Tomi to kill a mage of no little power. However, Tomi showed more zeal in seducing the mage's daughter, and kept delaying in fulfilling the order. The medusa fed up with this, and she decided to take matters into her own hands. During the ensuing turmoil, Medusa and the wizard killed each other, and Tomi was found guilty of killing them. I was good for his reputationa, but he become a wanted man for murdering the wizard. Finally, Tome decided to come to Neverwinter where one of his oldest friends, a forgery master, lives to make some documents and clear his name in Calimport. In Neverwinter, the rogue went to prison, but was quickly released.~/*C'est le dieu de l'endurance, de la souffrance et de la persévérance. Ilmater soigne ceux que les autres abandonnent. Nous demeurons pauvres, et collectons l'argent pour ceux qui en ont le plus besoin. Vous voyez, jai passé presque toutes mes années à Calimport au service dune puissante méduse. Elle était très importante dans la pègre de la ville, et ce nest pas rien, avec ou sans regard pétrifiant. Alors mon employeuse décida de prendre les choses en main elle-même. Ha, si javais su, je serais parti de Calimport bien plus tôt. Cest pourqoui je suis venu à Padhiver. Lun de mes vieux amis y habite, cest un maître faussaire ! Il devrait pouvoir me faire des documents pour minnocenter à Calimport.*/
